View and Manage a Model's Update History

A model can undergo many updates over its lifecycle. Factors like altered business circumstances, new data, improved settings motivate creating and deploying a new model version. To keep track of all these versions, examine a model's version history to know when it was updated by whom.

To view the update history:

* View a Prediction Definition in Model Manager.
* View a Model.
* In the side panel, click the History tab.
* In the Update History list, click the menu and choose the action you want.
